originalText.text: A friend of mine, who is a professional dancer, recommend Dr.Kim because I was having horrible neck pain. I was a little nervous at first because I never tried acupuncture, but Dr.Kim made me feel completely relaxed and comfortable. I really enjoyed my session and after just 30 mins my pain was gone. I couldn’t believe it! I definitely recommend trying acupuncture with Dr. Kim.
